Job Title: ETL Developer

Location: Piscataway, NJ

Employment Type: full-time

Listed Skills: Business Development, Sales

Description:
Dice is the leading career destination for tech experts at every stage of their careers. Our client, Wizard Tech Solutions Inc, is seeking the following. Apply via Dice today!

FindPro Group Inc. is a leading provider of on-demand talent solutions, specializing in streamlining the hiring process to quickly fill open positions with top-tier talent. We pride ourselves on our ability to align with our clients' unique requirements, providing innovative technology solutions to meet their needs.

Job Title: ETL DeveloperExperience Required: 6-10 yearsWork Location: Piscataway, NJPosition Type: Full-timeCompany: FindPro Group Inc.Visa Sponsorship: Available for the right candidates

Benefits:

Competitive salaryHealth, dental, and vision insurance401(k) retirement plan with company matchPaid time off and holidaysProfessional development and training opportunitiesVisa sponsorship for eligible candidates

Job Description: We are seeking a skilled ETL Developer with 6-10 years of experience to join our team in Piscataway, NJ. The ideal candidate will have a strong background in ETL development and data analysis. You will work closely with our clients to design, develop, and maintain ETL processes that meet their business needs.

Responsibilities:

Design, develop, and maintain ETL processes using tools such as Informatica, Talend, or SSISWork closely with business stakeholders to understand their data requirementsPerform data analysis to identify trends, patterns, and insightsOptimize ETL processes for performance and efficiencyDevelop and maintain documentation for ETL processes

Required Skills:

6-10 years of experience in ETL developmentStrong SQL skillsExperience with ETL tools such as Informatica, Talend, or SSISExperience with data analysis and data modelingStrong problem-solving and analytical skillsExcellent communication and interpersonal skills

Preferred Skills:

Experience with cloud-based ETL tools (e.g., AWS Glue, Azure Data Factory)Experience with big data technologies (e.g., Hadoop, Spark)Experience with data visualization tools (e.g., Tableau, Power BI)

If you meet the requirements and are interested in this exciting opportunity, please share your most updated resume to . We look forward to hearing from you!

Experience Level (if available): Entry level
